text.tspan: Clicking "Edit Event Info" will dropdown the "Add Event" options
When we add a new volunteer, their signout time is immediately assigned their signin time.
This way, volunteers do not accure hours until they sign out.
Drop-down times should segemented by 15mins, and only show valid time entries.
Valid time entries would be a signin / signout time during the event times +/- 1 or 2hrs.
Clicking Icon brings you to volunteer's full profile
Clicking Icon adds new volunteer entry
